{"tid":283520,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"公屋撚想領養貓","createTime":"2017-06-14T08:33:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T10:27:33.000Z","uid":41238,"like":9,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e1a3fd86e6cc1a5981901d66ba62a531924c7793","tid":283520,"uid":41238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T08:33:26.000Z","msg":"除愛協仲有咩機構可以俾公屋撚領養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打算聽日去愛協睇下 但想知仲有冇其他機構，我見好多貓義工都係公屋免問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇人有貓義工介紹係唔介意公屋撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（屋企已經裝晒窗網 成家都準備好想養隻貓仔）"},{"pid":"9611691ea1654a59cfbc5c2df25ff0ef0c1d2e1c","tid":283520,"uid":41238,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T08:37:02.000Z","msg":"負皮個個係咪啲好憎公屋撚嘅貓義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee953dbaab46455a038e62ca747be7bbb1fecdcf","tid":283520,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T08:45:29.000Z","msg":"FB好多領養貓貓page"},{"pid":"d5e6b40a5b3e051ff97405c9770cb62e16fbafea","tid":283520,"uid":41238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T08:48:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>FB好多領養貓貓page</blockquote><br />\n睇過晒 其實我以前去過好多呢啲領養活動 但知係公屋撚都好少會考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3351f7167f021476241719725992b39245e44f","tid":283520,"uid":62084,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T08:53:34.000Z","msg":"我都係facebook領養，都係影相比佢睇裝左貓網，準備左貓糧貓沙，<br />\n第一次去見下佢，第二次可以接佢返去，未家訪過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/14/165332_ca44390c91f6976ca786deea7ed61eb1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F14%2F165332_ca44390c91f6976ca786deea7ed61eb1.jpg&h=55aec8b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1dd33c495e76f27eea19f8ee5aa1478f40b7